    "description": "<strong>&quot;洗衣店模拟器&quot; 体验在忙碌而充满挑战的洗衣业中开展自己的事业。作为一家精品洗衣店的店主，你将处理从普通衣物到高档服饰的各种洗护需求，您还可以售卖各种洗衣店相关商品。管理好你的时间和资源，升级设备，优化店铺布局，并通过提供优质服务吸引更多顾客。</strong><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >顾客送来的脏衣服需要你一件件放入洗衣篮，然后装入洗衣机。别忘了，洗好的衣服还需烘干以保证质量和顾客满意度。</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/5899c9747daec187aaa49f01372b56fb.poster.avif?t=1763086043\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/5899c9747daec187aaa49f01372b56fb.webm?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/5899c9747daec187aaa49f01372b56fb.mp4?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在你的洗衣店内，不仅提供洗涤服务，还可以经营洗衣相关产品。精心选择商品，合理定价，然后将它们一件件摆放到货架上，吸引顾客购买。</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/975b9c1456a5f251d023e42f548e0dc7.poster.avif?t=1763086043\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/975b9c1456a5f251d023e42f548e0dc7.webm?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/975b9c1456a5f251d023e42f548e0dc7.mp4?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >快速而精确的收银是提高顾客满意度的关键。你需要熟练地扫描商品并找零。随着生意的扩展，你甚至可以聘请一名收银员来帮助你应对日益增长的客流。</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/0ff1135f87ef6c45cf3883854b0088b6.poster.avif?t=1763086043\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/0ff1135f87ef6c45cf3883854b0088b6.webm?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/0ff1135f87ef6c45cf3883854b0088b6.mp4?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >提供快速优质的服务，以确保顾客在取回洗好的衣物时感到满意。快速的服务不仅能保持顾客的忠诚，还可能赢得额外的小费。</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/db73759d203fdf0739dbe9a7f4f6d974.poster.avif?t=1763086043\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/db73759d203fdf0739dbe9a7f4f6d974.webm?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/db73759d203fdf0739dbe9a7f4f6d974.mp4?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >保持店铺的清洁和整洁至关重要。除了日常的打扫，你还可以用滚筒刷重新设计店内的墙面和地板，定制你自己的洗衣店风格，创建一个让顾客愿意回来的环境。</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/a453a2e3153dc1c4a8846d658dfb9a22.poster.avif?t=1763086043\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/a453a2e3153dc1c4a8846d658dfb9a22.webm?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/a453a2e3153dc1c4a8846d658dfb9a22.mp4?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随着业务的不断扩展，你将解锁新的商店面积，扩大你的洗衣店产业。优化你的服务和设施，让顾客络绎不绝。</h2></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/a0ef32ca9faca345bd20f3065f481bf3.poster.avif?t=1763086043\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/a0ef32ca9faca345bd20f3065f481bf3.webm?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125570/extras/a0ef32ca9faca345bd20f3065f481bf3.mp4?t=1763086043\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随着你的业务增长，你可以雇佣各种熟练的帮手，包括洗衣专家、烘干技师和地面清洁工以及搬货员和补货员等，他们将成为你成功的重要支持。</h2></strong>",
